title: Tues Post Show (10-25-22)
itunes:title: Tues Post Show (10-25-22)
description:
Bobby gives an update after his mouth surgery. Bobby learned the difference between a dentist and an endodontist. Bobby explains the reason you may see him putting his hand underneath his shirt in videos. We talk about Leslie Jordan who passed away in a car crash yesterday. Why gamers have better memories than those who don’t play. Why most reviews online are negative. Bobby updates on if he will write another kid’s book.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
